on-departure: ideology = "liberal"; liberal_strength += 8; liberal_dissent -= 10; left_dissent += 5; moderate_dissent += 5; pfjp_relation += 3 if ( pfjp_leader = "Ricter" ); pfjp_relation -= 3 if ( pfjp_leader = "Suheil" );


The <span style="color: #03c2fc;">**Liberals**</span>, led by Albin Clavin, support capitalism, privatization and collaboration with ATO countries.

