The <span style="color: #6e377a;">**Moderates**</span> are not quite as skeptical of Sollism and support collaboration with the rest of the <span style="color: #6e377a;">**USP**</span>.

@changed
on-arrival: left_dissent += 5; liberal_dissent += 5; moderate_dissent += 5;

We have changed ideologies. Many in the party feel unmoored.
